# Voice — `<Company Name>`

How this company *talks*. Astra's creator sub-agent loads this file
when generating any artifact for the company and uses it as a hard
constraint on tone, sentence shape, and word choice.

This is narrative on purpose. Don't try to compress it to a JSON
schema — the LLM internalizes the *feel* better from prose.

