## Words and phrases the company NEVER uses

Beyond the structured `forbidden_phrases` in brand.yml — narrative
notes on *why* certain things are off-limits. Helps the LLM
generalize, not just match strings.

- We never call ourselves "AI-powered" — every modern product uses AI.
  Saying so is no longer a differentiator. Describe what it *does*
  instead.
- We don't say "revolutionary" or "disruptive" — overused, hollow.
- <Company-specific aversions>

